tags: [[Special Rule]]
title: Eternal Warrior
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

If a model with this special rule suffers an unsaved Wound from an attack that inflicted [[Instant Death]], it only reduces its Wounds by 1, instead of automatically reducing its Wounds to 0.